Weather test application README

Weather test application uses https://openweathermap.org/ API to get a weather data either by city or by geographical coordinates.

Installation and running:
--------------------------------------------------
1. mvn install.  
2. mvn spring-boot:run


Usage:
--------------------------------------------------
1.Start application
2.Open web page on localhost:8080
3.Authorize in a login form, using following names and passwords: eugene/eugene, dmitri/dmitri, oleg/oleg, roman/roman.
4.On the left control pane enter a city name and press "GET WEATHER" button    
5.On the right control pane enter latitude and longitude and press "GET WEATHER" button
6.Change user using "logout" link

